/*
 * $Header: /users/source/archives/vile.vcs/RCS/config.emx,v 1.2 1999/12/29 23:09:24 tom Exp $
 *
 * hand-generated configuration for EMX (gcc) on OS/2
 *
 * This assumes the termcap library which comes bundled with EMX.  It will
 * build a minimally-functional version of vile:
 *	(a) arrow- and function-keys do not work
 *	(b) the screensize is 24x80
 *	(c) colors are (well not good)
 * You should use the configure script, with ncurses 5.0 to solve these
 * problems.
 */

